# League mode talks to the YesGaffa Supabase project, but only through the
# isolated `sweepstake` schema (RPC gateway). Copy this to `.env` and fill in
# the YesGaffa project's values. Leave them unset to run quick-play only.
#
# The `sweepstake` schema must be added to the project's exposed schemas
# (Supabase dashboard -> Settings -> API -> Exposed schemas) for these RPCs to
# be reachable. This is additive and does not affect YesGaffa.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
